# Base32 TOTP seed for the test account's authenticator.
# This is the same secret an authenticator app stores when you scan the
# enrollment QR code (the "Set up key" / "manual entry" string).
#
# Copy this file to .env (which is gitignored), fill in a real test-account
# secret, and load it in your test runner. NEVER commit a real secret.
MFA_TOTP_SECRET=JBSWY3DPEHPK3PXP
